						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0ABluefin Tuna Get It On off North Carolina%0D%0AEvidence is mounting that Atlantic bluefin tuna spawn in a patch of ocean called the Slope Sea. Will the controversial discovery upend how the prized fish are managed?%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/bluefin-tuna-get-it-on-off-north-carolina/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



